'''The Montana Kaimin''' is the [[University Of Montana|University of Montana]]'s student-run independent newspaper located in [[Missoula, Montana|Missoula, MT]]. The daily paper is printed four times a week, Tuesday through Friday, with special editions printed occasionally. The current editor-in-chief is Roman Stubbs.<ref>http://www.montanakaimin.com/about-us</ref> The newspaper is divided into five section including news, sports, outdoors, opinion, arts and culture.
